            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <h4>快速介绍</h4><p>秋季促销就快过去咯，你买了吗？这周又有一大波新游戏上架啦！（而且还全都堆在12月1日）</p><p>本周的游戏有：<a href="https://indienova.com/u/%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B4%25A5%25E9%2598%259F%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%2588%258F" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">队友游戏</a>出品<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/857950/Incredible_Mandy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《不可思议之梦蝶》</a>、主角可以制造平台砖块的2D游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/833980/Dave/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《Dave》</a>、<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/606280/Darksiders_III/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《暗黑血统 III》</a>、<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/798420/Professional_Fishing/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《专业钓鱼》</a>、<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/392160/X4_Foundations/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《X4: 基奠》</a>。</p><h4>The Crown of Leaves</h4><p>关键词：视觉小说、点击</p><p>发售日期：11月27日</p><p>Roui 在城市中遭受了挫折，回到他的吉普赛故乡，重新捡起珠宝工艺活。然而一个神秘的手镯订单，开始让他的生活变得越来越不寻常……</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/The Crown of Leaves1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10781" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/The Crown of Leaves2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10782" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/The Crown of Leaves3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10783" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/604330/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Broken Reality</h4><p>关键词：步行模拟、网络</p><p>发售日期：11月29日</p><p>上一次在 Guide 中提到这个游戏已经是9.24-9.30那期了……直接就跳票了两个月！这次肯定是真的要发售了！站内有一篇文章详细介绍过它：<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/your-life-inside-a-browser/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《当你的人生被塞进了一款浏览器》</a></p><p>在未来，超级公司 NATEM 掌握了绝大部分的数字服务的控制权，包括平民老百姓的电脑和互联网都受控于 NATEM。NATEM 将我们2D 的电脑屏幕界限破除，现在你的周身环境便是网站浏览器了。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9693" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9692" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Broken Reality3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9694" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/757480/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>How Mosquito Became Human</h4><p>关键词：平台、搞笑</p><p>发售日期：12月1日</p><p>呃，其实这个质量一般不会被选进 guide 里，但是看到这游戏的标题（再加上被蚊子咬了），就决定介绍一下！！游戏规则非常简单，你必须要变得更大！为此进食吧，你吃啥就会变成啥。第一步就是从蚊子变成小青蛙，接着是鸟、企鹅、狗……每一个阶段都有不同的操作特征，为了找到下一个被吃的生物群系要在关卡之间穿越。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/How Mosquito Became Human1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10784" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/How Mosquito Became Human2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10785" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/862230/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Escape Doodland</h4><p>关键词：欢乐、平台跳跃、困难</p><p>发售日期：12月1日</p><p>怪物突然出现在了涂鸦世界！要么跑，要么死！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Escape Doodland1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10786" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Escape Doodland2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10787" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Escape Doodland3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10788" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/670930/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Superfighters Deluxe</h4><p>关键词：单机&amp;多人、暴力、动作</p><p>发售日期：12月1日</p><p>有一点像要素丰富的《鸭王争霸》，利用关卡中的武器及各种物体击倒敌人！游戏同时支持1-8人混战，1-4人生存模式，关卡编辑器等等。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Superfighters Deluxe.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10789" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/855860/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Simmiland</h4><p>关键词：创世神、模拟经营</p><p>发售日期：12月1日（steam 审核问题可能跳票，建议走<a href="https://sokpop.itch.io/simmiland" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">itch 购买</a>）</p><p>每月两个实验游戏的 <a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/artitst-collective/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Sokpop</a> 团队出品！在陆地上利用手中的卡牌，创造生命和文明吧！可选的卡牌包含生物、天气、行为等等，由你来决定世界的演化！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Simmiland1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10790" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Simmiland2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10791" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/932850/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Hotel Sowls</h4><p>关键词：解谜、点击</p><p>发售日期：本周（抢先体验）</p><p>来自韩国的学生团队作品（貌似是毕设），游戏支持韩文&amp;英文。</p><p>主角是一名药剂师，偶然从新闻得知一种会发出声音的神秘宝石，便因此踏上了寻找的旅程。成功找到之后，主角却在休息的酒店中遗失了珍贵的宝石。明显是有人将其偷走了……四处探索这间酒店吧，到底有什么秘密？你能否成功寻回宝石呢？多条剧情分支等待着你。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Hotel Sowls1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10792" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Hotel Sowls2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10793" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/Hotel Sowls3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10794" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/968350/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>THE ENIGMA MACHINE</h4><p>关键词：科幻、恐怖、解谜</p><p>发售日期：12月1日（可能跳票）</p><p>你可曾好奇人工智能的脑袋里都在想些什么？DREAMSCAPE 帮你实现这个愿望！以交互式的 3D 环境展现你的 AI 好朋友的精神世界，但要注意，探索受污染的 AI 可能会导致不可预测的结果。游戏流程1-2小时，作者在商店页特别提示：除非你看到 Credits 菜单，游戏就还没有结束。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/THE ENIGMA MACHINE2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10795" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/THE ENIGMA MACHINE1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10796" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/11/THE ENIGMA MACHINE3-2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="10799" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/977810/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>

